name: enchantment.lootBonus
description: Mobs will drop more loot when killed.

name: enchantment.arrowFire
description: Arrows fired from the bow will deal additional fire damage.

name: enchantment.waterWorker
description: Increases mining speed while underwater.

name: enchantment.protect.all
description: Reduces damage from most sources.

name: enchantment.mending
description: Repairs the durability of armor and tools with EXP.

name: enchantment.damage.undead
description: Increases damage against undead mobs such as zombies and skeletons.

name: enchantment.fire
description: Causes additional fire damage when used to attack a mob.

name: enchantment.knockback
description: Increases the knockback strength of the weapon.

name: enchantment.waterWalker
description: Increases movement speed while under water.

name: enchantment.arrowDamage
description: Increases the damage of arrows fired from the bow.

name: enchantment.lootBonusFishing
description: Increases the chance of getting good loot while fishing.

name: enchantment.oxygen
description: Extends the amount of time the player can spend under water. Also improves vision while under water.

name: enchantment.protect.fall
description: Reduces fall damage and ender pearl teleportation damage.

name: enchantment.damage.arthropods
description: Increases damage against arthropods such as Spiders and Silverfish.

name: enchantment.thorns
description: Causes damage to enemies when they attack you.

name: enchantment.untouching
description: Allows fragile blocks such as glass to be collected.

name: enchantment.arrowKnockback
description: Increases the knockback strength of arrows fired by the bow.

name: enchantment.damage.all
description: Increases the damage of the item.

name: enchantment.frostWalker
description: Freezes water under the player into cracked ice.

name: enchantment.arrowInfinite
description: Allows the bow to fire normal arrows for free. You must have at least one arrow for this to work.

name: enchantment.vanishing_curse
description: Destroyes the enchanted item if you die with it in your inventory.

name: enchantment.digging
description: Increases mining speed of the tool.

name: enchantment.lootBonusDigger
description: Some blocks like coal and diamond ore may drop additional items.

name: enchantment.binding_curse
description: Prevents the enchanted item from being removed from an armor slot.

name: enchantment.protect.projectile
description: Reduces damage from projectiles such as arrows and fire balls.

name: enchantment.protect.fire
description: Reduces the effects of fire damage. Also reduces the burn time when set on fire.

name: enchantment.durability
description: Causes the tool to lose durability at a slower rate.

name: enchantment.fishingSpeed
description: Decreases the amount of time it takes for a fish to bite the hook.

name: enchantment.sweeping
description: Increases the damage of sweeping attacks.

name: enchantment.protect.explosion
description: Reduces damage from explosions and explosion knockback.
